title: Riverhounds' Vincent, Kerr earn spots on All-League soccer teams
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Post: Sports - Today 
The United Soccer League has awarded two Pittsburgh Riverhounds players spots on the 2015 All-League teams, the league announced today....
